MOHD. MUSHEER 
AI/ML Engineer (Fresher) 
Amravati, Maharashtra, India 
Phone: +91 9370086707 
Email: musheerayan@gmail.com 
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohdmusheer 
GitHub: https://github.com/mohd-musheer 
SUMMARY 
Entry-level AI/ML Engineer with hands-on experience in machine learning and deep learning using 
Python, Scikit-learn, and PyTorch. Skilled in data preprocessing, feature engineering, model training, 
evaluation, and deployment using FastAPI and Docker. Passionate about building end-to-end AI 
solutions for real-world problems. 
TECHNICAL SKILLS 
Programming Languages: Python, SQL, R, C++ 
Machine Learning: Scikit-learn, Regression, Classification, Random Forest 
Deep Learning: PyTorch  
Data Analysis: NumPy, Pandas 
Data Visualization: Matplotlib, Seaborn 
Model Deployment: FastAPI, Docker, Render 
Tools: Git, GitHub, VS Code, Jupyter Notebook 
EDUCATION 
Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA) (Final Year) 
Takshashila Mahavidyalaya, Amravati 
Expected Graduation:  May-2026 
CERTIFICATIONS 
Python – Udemy | Machine Learning – Udemy | SQL – Udemy 
PROJECT EXPERIENCE 
AI Vision – CIFAR-10 Image Classifier (Accuracy: 88%) (GitHub) (Live) 
• Built a deep learning image classifier using ResNet18 (PyTorch) for 10-class object recognition. 
• Implemented FastAPI for real-time inference with an interactive web UI. 
• Dockerized and deployed the application to the cloud for production use. 
AI Employee Attrition Predictor (Accuracy: 84%) (GitHub) (Live) 
• Developed a Random Forest ML model to predict employee attrition (stay/leave). 
• Performed data preprocessing, feature encoding, and class imbalance handling using Scikit-learn. 
• Deployed the system using FastAPI and Docker with a user-friendly UI. 
Playing Card Image Classifier (Accuracy: ~95%) (Github) (Live) 
• Implemented an image classification model using EfficientNet-B0 (PyTorch) with transfer learning. 
• Classified 53 playing card categories, including Joker, with high accuracy. 
• Exposed predictions via FastAPI and packaged the project using Docker. 
LANGUAGES 
English | Hindi | Marathi 
INTERESTS    
Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Model Deployment, Learning New Tools
